\"zDocsExportItem zDocsExportTopicButton\" href=\"#\" id=\"singlePdf\" role=\"button\">Save selected topic</a><a class=\"zDocsExportItem zDocsExportSubtopicsButton\" href=\"#\" id=\"pdfWithChildren\" role=\"button\">Save selected topic and subtopics</a><a class=\"zDocsExportItem zDocsExportBundleButton\" href=\"#\" id=\"wholeBundlePdf\" role=\"button\">Save entire publication</a></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicShare zDocsShareButton\" role=\"listitem\"><span aria-expanded=\"false\" aria-label=\"Share\" class=\"d-none d-lg-flex zDocsShareDialogButton\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" data-tooltip-content=\"Share\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsTopicActionsTooltip\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-share\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-share\"></use></svg></span><span class=\"d-lg-none zDocsShareDialogButton\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-share\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-share\"></use></svg>Share</span><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu\"><a class=\"dropdown-item zDocsShareButton zDocsShareEmail\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\"><span>Email Link</span></a><a class=\"dropdown-item zDocsShareButton zDocsShareLink\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\"><span>Copy Link</span></a></div></div><div class=\"zDocsFeedback zDocsFeedback zDocsTopicFeedback\" role=\"listitem\"><span aria-label=\"Feedback\" class=\"zDocsFeedbackButton d-none d-lg-flex\" data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_main_7421057\" data-toggle=\"modal\" data-tooltip-content=\"Feedback\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsTopicActionsTooltip\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg></span><span class=\"d-lg-none d-flex zDocsFeedbackButton\" data-backdrop=\"static\" data-return-focus=\"#zDocsTopicActionsMobile\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_main_7421057\" data-toggle=\"modal\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Juli 10, 2024</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104haz1719555440417.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/haz1719555440417.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/haz1719555440417.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"prt1665703007461\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">\n      $fieldindb\n </h1>\n<div class=\"body conbody\" id=\"prt1665703007461___fieldindb_263818\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Check whether a field is a database field, or not.\n </p>\n<section class=\"section refsyn\" id=\"prt1665703007461__topic_d83114e1_d83115e1_d83116e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"prt1665703007461__p_d83117e1_d83118e1_d83119e1\">\n<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$fieldindb</span> { <code class=\"ph codeph\">(</code>\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">Field</var>\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">)</code> }</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"prt1665703007461__topic_d54907e1_d54908e1_d54909e1_d54910e1_d54911e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d380720e75\">\n                       \n Parameters\n </h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"3\" id=\"prt1665703007461__table_d8522e1_d8523e1_d8524e1\"><caption><span class=\"table--title-label\">Table 1. </span><span class=\"title\">Parameters</span></caption><colgroup><col/><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"prt1665703007461__table_d8522e1_d8523e1_d8524e1__entry__1\">\n Parameter\n </th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"prt1665703007461__table_d8522e1_d8523e1_d8524e1__entry__2\">\n Data Type\n </th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"prt1665703007461__table_d8522e1_d8523e1_d8524e1__entry__3\">\n Description\n </th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"prt1665703007461__table_d8522e1_d8523e1_d8524e1__entry__1\">\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">Field</var>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"prt1665703007461__table_d8522e1_d8523e1_d8524e1__entry__2\">\n String\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"prt1665703007461__table_d8522e1_d8523e1_d8524e1__entry__3\">Field name; optional. It can optionally contain\n                        a qualified field name, for example <code class=\"ph codeph\">MYFLD.MYENT</code>. If\n                        omitted, the current field is used; in this case,\n                           <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$fieldindb</span> can be used only in field-level triggers. </td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"prt1665703007461__topic_d54912e1_d54913e1_d54914e1_d54915e1_d54916e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d380720e135\">\n                       \n Return Values\n </h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"prt1665703007461__table_d8525e1_d8526e1_d8527e1\"><caption><span class=\"table--title-label\">Table 2. </span><span class=\"title\">Values returned by <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$fieldindb</span>\n</span></caption><colgroup><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"prt1665703007461__table_d8525e1_d8526e1_d8527e1__entry__1\" rowspan=\"1\">\n Value \n </th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"prt1665703007461__table_d8525e1_d8526e1_d8527e1__entry__2\" rowspan=\"1\">\n Meaning\n </th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"prt1665703007461__table_d8525e1_d8526e1_d8527e1__entry__1\" rowspan=\"1\">\n 1\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"prt1665703007461__table_d8525e1_d8526e1_d8527e1__entry__2\" rowspan=\"1\">\n The field is a database field (TRUE).\n </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"prt1665703007461__table_d8525e1_d8526e1_d8527e1__entry__1\" rowspan=\"1\">\n 0\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"prt1665703007461__table_d8525e1_d8526e1_d8527e1__entry__2\" rowspan=\"1\">\n The field is not a database field (FALSE).\n </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"prt1665703007461__table_d8525e1_d8526e1_d8527e1__entry__1\" rowspan=\"1\">\n \"\"\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"prt1665703007461__table_d8525e1_d8526e1_d8527e1__entry__2\" rowspan=\"1\">\n An error occurred.\n </td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"prt1665703007461__p_d83126e1_d83127e1_d83128e1\">If an error occurs, <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$procerror</span> contains a negative value that identifies the exact error.</p>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"3\" id=\"prt1665703007461__table_d8528e1_d8529e1_d8530e1\"><caption><span class=\"table--title-label\">Table 3. </span><span class=\"title\">Values of $procerror Commonly Returned Following Field-Level ProcScript Functions</span></caption><colgroup><col/><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"prt1665703007461__table_d8528e1_d8529e1_d8530e1__entry__1\">Value </th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"prt1665703007461__table_d8528e1_d8529e1_d8530e1__entry__2\">\nError\nconstant\n</th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"prt1665703007461__table_d8528e1_d8529e1_d8530e1__entry__3\">\nMeaning\n</th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"prt1665703007461__table_d8528e1_d8529e1_d8530e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">-1101\n</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"prt1665703007461__table_d8528e1_d8529e1_d8530e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">&lt;UPROCERR_FIELD&gt;\n</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"prt1665703007461__table_d8528e1_d8529e1_d8530e1__entry__3\">\nAn incorrect\nfield name was provided; either the field name is not valid syntactically\nor the field is not available in the component.\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"prt1665703007461__topic_d54917e1_d54918e1_d54919e1_d54920e1_d54921e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d380720e262\">Use</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"prt1665703007461__d5916e20\">Allowed in all component types.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"prt1665703007461__topic_d54922e1_d54923e1_d54924e1_d54925e1_d54926e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d380720e272\">\n                       \n Description\n </h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"prt1665703007461__p_d83138e1_d83139e1_d83140e1\">The function <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$fieldindb</span> returns an indication if a field is a database field, that is, if the <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Is External</span> property of the component field is <code class=\"ph codeph\">T</code>.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"prt1665703007461__section_r2x_rgp_wbc\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d380720e290\">Example: Setting Video Attribute of a Field</h2>\n<p class=\"p\">The following ProcScript causes MYFIELD to blink if it is a database\n            field:</p>\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre language-plaintext\" id=\"prt1665703007461__pre_bdz_sgp_wbc\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">if ($fieldindb(MYFIELD.MYENTITY))\n fieldvideo MYFIELD.MYENTITY, \"BLI\"\nendif\n</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/jfn1665702577202.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>$fieldname</a><p>Return the name of the current field or check for the presence of a specified field in the component.</p></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_7421057\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_7421057\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "$fieldindb Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Juli 10, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 $fieldindb Check whether a field is a database field, or not. $fieldindb { ( Field ) } Parameters Table 1. Parameters Parameter Data Type Description Field String Field name; optional. It can optionally contain a qualified field name, for example MYFLD.MYENT . If omitted, the current field is used; in this case, $fieldindb can be used only in field-level triggers. Return Values Table 2. Values returned by $fieldindb Value Meaning 1 The field is a database field (TRUE). 0 The field is not a database field (FALSE). \"\" An error occurred. If an error occurs, $procerror contains a negative value that identifies the exact error. Table 3. Values of $procerror Commonly Returned Following Field-Level ProcScript Functions Value Error constant Meaning -1101 <UPROCERR_FIELD> An incorrect field name was provided; either the field name is not valid syntactically or the field is not available in the component. Use Allowed in all component types. Description The function $fieldindb returns an indication if a field is a database field, that is, if the Is External property of the component field is T . Example: Setting Video Attribute of a Field The following ProcScript causes MYFIELD to blink if it is a database field: if ($fieldindb(MYFIELD.MYENTITY)) fieldvideo MYFIELD.MYENTITY, \"BLI\" endif Copy Related Links $fieldname Return the name of the current field or check for the presence of a specified field in the component. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}